Digital Lending

Digital Lending supports the end-to-end lending lifecycle across all retail loan products and channels in a unified lending platform. Create a loan application process that suits the needs of your clients, both self-service application intake and assisted application intake.

Use a new data model that supports the loan process across all consumer loan products. Provide lenders and clients with an easy-to-navigate loan application experience by using scalable integrations and native capabilities for product catalog, eligibility, and pricing.

Give Clients a Self-Serve Loan Application Process
Your clients can apply for a loan during a time that’s convenient for them by using Digital Lending self-service application intake.

Help Clients Apply for a Loan
Digital Lending assisted application intake experience provides your bankers with a seamless loan application process.

Approve or Reject a Loan Application by Using Underwriter Console
Give underwriters easy access to loan application details to make informed decisions.
